VERSION 0.5.1, 10/14/2015.

Updates:
- Updated samtools and bcftools to version 1.2,
  with new variant calling option [-m]
- Updated platypus to take a file of target 
  regions [-r]
- Fixed minor issues with GATK variant calling


VERSION 0.5.0, 03/31/2015. 
Initial release.

Platform
============
1. Illumina single-end or paired-end sequencing

Genomes
============
1. Homo sapiens (hg19)

Aligners
============
1. BWA aln
2. BWA mem
3. Novoalign

Variant callers
============
1. GATK HaplotypeCaller
2. GATK UnifiiedGenotyper
3. FreeBayes
4. SAMtools mpileup/bcftools
5. Issac Variant Caller (IVC)
6. Platypus

